        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Late chunking processes one document at a time \u2014 each full document is a single encoder call. To maximise GPU utilisation, use a multi-threaded or async worker pool that processes several documents concurrently. Each worker owns a copy of the model or sends requests to the Jina API in parallel, then writes resulting vectors to a shared FAISS index in a thread-safe batch insert."
